* &quot;Dickie Roberts: Former Child Star&quot; (2003) (cameo)
* &quot;Robot Chicken&quot; (2006) (Episode 2.2, &quot;Federated Resources&quot;)
* &quot;The Two Coreys&quot; (2007–2008) (TV series)
* &quot;Lost Boys: The Tribe&quot; (2008)

